name: tracey pooh
body: Another successful ride! We had five riders total and mostly kept in a relatively close together group for most of the ride. It was sunny and warm, and the pace was fast (thanks to the 3 non-leader riders being *very* strong and fast). So Hunter and I mostly tried to hold on as best we could and make our legs get in some really good training. No flats!

name: tracey pooh
body:
Ride Stats:
5 riders (2 were leaders)
Finish times range: 6hr 25min to 6hr 45min
